xtc.lang
Class CFeatureExtractor

java.lang.Object
  xtc.tree.Visitor
      xtc.lang.CFeatureExtractor

public class CFeatureExtractor
extends Visitor

A visitor to extract C features. This visitor assumes that the AST is well-typed and annotated with the correct types.

Version:
$Revision: 1.6 $
